{"tid":1809717,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙田區議會為反修例事件死者默哀 兩名少數派議員離席","createTime":"2020-01-03T09:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T12:03:45.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f5af5ae2e3c5ceb01268304af3d474c06ee0b7c6","tid":1809717,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"沙田區區議會召開首次會議，區議員陸梓峂動議為反修例事件中犧牲的人士默哀一分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n議員莫錦貴說，今次事件的死傷者不只反修例人士，亦包括被磚頭擲傷不治的清潔工人，認為不能只為部分人默哀，內心亦不舒服，另一名議員林港坤亦表示認同，兩人之後在其他議員站立默哀期間離開會議室 。<br />\n<br />\n有議員質疑在場列席的民政事務專員陳婉雯未有參與默哀，陳婉雯解釋有關行動是政治表態，是否參與只是個人選擇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500861-20200103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500861-20200103.htm&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7AFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=1509af71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500861-20200103.htm&h=fdfba02f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500861-20200103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"02abf6cd25b4b4f18aaeccdc78c263bfe8df4fe7","tid":1809717,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"少數派議員係度玩政治<br />\n唔搞民生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367d1cafa1248642ae9273cb6277eff55d3d5f32","tid":1809717,"uid":64757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"不尊重場合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0148e0cf72afa164d5b04bb09d0e430569ed55b0","tid":1809717,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d67fd00a7a791bfd5471257af2fb21a1cf5f6d4","tid":1809717,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"少數派好撚麻煩，又唔做嘢又唔讀